A notable supporter of the All Progressives Congress (APC) presidential candidate in the north, Babachir Lawal, has warned Asiwaju Bola Tinubu that Muslim/Muslim ticket is not feasible in Nigeria, stating that the decision is dead on arrival to northern Christians.
The former Secretary to the Government of the Federation (SGF), therefore, told the APC presidential candidate, Tinubu, to erase any plan  of a Muslim/Muslim ticket if he wants to win the 2023  presidential election.
